{
  "texts": [
    "Specifically, when presented with the PLAY client request, LLMPF first matches it with the corresponding grammar.",
    "To expedite the matching process, we maintain the grammar corpus in the map format: G = {type → grammar}.",
    "Here, type represents the types of client requests.",
    "LLMPF uses the first line of each grammar as the label for message types.",
    "The grammar corresponds to the concrete message grammar."
  ]
}